{"tid":2111282,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"「新人入議會發揮更大作用」 莫乃光棄選I.T.界 交棒黃浩華戰建制","createTime":"2020-07-16T12:19:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-16T12:35:49.000Z","uid":25558,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"cf06ca4781b72ed03f9fec835d5a568a4d25ee38","tid":2111282,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T12:19:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200716/DFW6ZZUUV77BJHNUZ4CL2RCHKM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200716%2FDFW6ZZUUV77BJHNUZ4CL2RCHKM%2F&d=q%2BUwj3SihaKoadPXZHTFacTiFwqRwBg1VWT7Je45URE%3D&h=7e24ec52\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200716%2FDFW6ZZUUV77BJHNUZ4CL2RCHKM%2F&h=38a87485\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200716/DFW6ZZUUV77BJHNUZ4CL2RCHKM/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n「新人入議會發揮更大作用」<br />\n莫乃光棄選I.T.界 交棒黃浩華戰建制<br />\n<br />\n【新聞焦點】<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】本屆立會多名舊將告別，包括2012年起出任資訊科技界議員至今的莫乃光。他接受本報訪問時強調，棄戰與港版國安法無關，純因發現有較自己更適合出任議員的年輕人，認為對方能在來屆議會發揮更大作用。據了解，接替莫代表民主派出戰的是民主派I.T.界選委、零時政府網站發起人黃浩華。建制陣營盛傳派網上烹飪平台DayDayCook（日日煮）創辦人朱嘉盈挑戰。<br />\n<br />\n記者：林俊謙<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/JXXU6t1o8UqdDBKnTSdPDtFx0DY=/747x946/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/7IUNY5SQN7MCR7ETFAB2QXFHUY.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FJXXU6t1o8UqdDBKnTSdPDtFx0DY%3D%2F747x946%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F7IUNY5SQN7MCR7ETFAB2QXFHUY.gif&h=797846ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n莫乃光2012年起出任資訊科技界議員，昨宣佈將交棒年輕一代。<br />\n<br />\n莫乃光接受訪問時。。。。。。。。。。。。「但問題唔係我有冇能力、體力、意志，而係呢四年係咪有更好嘅人，可以做啲我做唔到嘅嘢」。透露早前與民主派資訊科技界選委溝通時，感到現時是最佳時間交棒，希望界內選民「畀啲信心新一代嘅人」。<br />\n<br />\n他稱離開議會後會先。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/2N3xwBUU6d2R5tlaZ_88QsGGZw0=/190x154/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/76AMDLJE5Z5PCPHXBHOCZJBE3M.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F2N3xwBUU6d2R5tlaZ_88QsGGZw0%3D%2F190x154%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F76AMDLJE5Z5PCPHXBHOCZJBE3M.gif&h=3cc6fbb0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n黃浩華<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n冀立會終可取消功能組別<br />\n<br />\n莫乃光訪問其間極「口密」，拒透露接棒人，形容對方是一位出色的年輕人， 「如果大家都諗界內精英、江湖大佬先適合坐（議員）呢啲位，我覺得係不合時宜」。據本報了解，近日曾與莫乃光在fb直播的32歲I.T.界選委、數據專才黃浩華會接棒出戰。據網上資料，黃為軟件工程師、香港開放數據諮詢委員會代表，近期曾在網上講解。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n建制派盛傳由38歲、2012年創立烹飪平台DayDayCook（日日煮）的朱嘉盈挑戰。網上資料顯示，朱2015年開展中國市場，2017年曾完成第三輪一億元人民幣融資，由K11鄭志剛、阿里巴巴創業者基金領投。朱前年曾參加訪京團，獲副總理韓正接見。本報曾向朱查詢是否有意參選，昨晚未獲回覆。"},{"pid":"254f7c0b88576e4d4407958443d04060258691c6","tid":2111282,"uid":146285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T12:20:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"768d35c0c7ff3f81365e25b66c8b416ac9347bb2","tid":2111282,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T12:30:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c25a1eff2897c28a59bef5187fcdc507c65cc37","tid":2111282,"uid":61280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T12:35:49.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">等睇呢班扮民功撚／大愛支又玩轉世當交棒！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></span></strong>"}]}